#. <section class="sutta" id="sn15.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn15.4:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 15"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 15"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. The First Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 4. Khīrasutta → mātuthaññasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn15.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Khīrasutta"
msgstr "4. Mother’s Milk"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.181"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn15.4:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn15.4:1.2"
msgid "“Anamataggoyaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃsāro."
msgstr "“Mendicants, transmigration has no known beginning."

msgctxt "sn15.4:1.3"
msgid ""
"Pubbā koṭi na paññāyati avijjānīvaraṇānaṃ sattānaṃ taṇhāsaṃyojanānaṃ "
"sandhāvataṃ saṃsarataṃ."
msgstr ""
"No first point is found of sentient beings roaming and transmigrating, "
"hindered by ignorance and fettered by craving."

msgctxt "sn15.4:1.4"
msgid ""
"Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ, yaṃ vā vo iminā "
"dīghena addhunā sandhāvataṃ saṃsarataṃ mātuthaññaṃ pītaṃ, yaṃ vā catūsu "
"mahāsamuddesu udakan”ti?"
msgstr ""
"What do you think? Which is more: the mother’s milk you’ve drunk while "
"roaming and transmigrating for such a very long time, or the water in the "
"four oceans?”"

msgctxt "sn15.4:1.5"
msgid ""
"“Yathā kho mayaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā dhammaṃ desitaṃ ājānāma, etadeva, "
"bhante, bahutaraṃ yaṃ no iminā dīghena addhunā sandhāvataṃ saṃsarataṃ "
"mātuthaññaṃ pītaṃ, na tveva catūsu mahāsamuddesu udakan”ti."
msgstr ""
"“As we understand the Buddha’s teaching, the mother’s milk we’ve drunk while "
"roaming and transmigrating is more than the water in the four oceans.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn15.4:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Sādhu sādhu, bhikkhave, sādhu kho me tumhe, bhikkhave, evaṃ dhammaṃ desitaṃ "
"ājānātha."
msgstr ""
"“Good, good, mendicants! It’s good that you understand my teaching like this."

msgctxt "sn15.4:2.2"
msgid ""
"Etadeva, bhikkhave, bahutaraṃ yaṃ vo iminā dīghena addhunā sandhāvataṃ "
"saṃsarataṃ mātuthaññaṃ pītaṃ, na tveva catūsu mahāsamuddesu udakaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The mother’s milk you’ve drunk while roaming and transmigrating for such a "
"very long time is more than the water in the four oceans."

msgctxt "sn15.4:2.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "sn15.4:2.4"
msgid "Anamataggoyaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃsāro … pe …"
msgstr "Transmigration has no known beginning. …"

msgctxt "sn15.4:2.5"
msgid "alaṃ vimuccitun”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is quite enough for you to become disillusioned, dispassionate, and "
"freed regarding all conditions.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn15.4:2.6"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
